# Packaging rules for the rfc skill (see package.sh / scripts/package.py).
# gitignore-style globs, one per line. '#' starts a comment; a leading '!'
# re-includes something an earlier rule dropped. Patterns are matched against
# the shipped rfc/ subtree — build tooling and dev-meta live outside it and
# are never packaged in the first place.

__pycache__
*.pyc
*.pyo
.DS_Store
